50|$|In 2007, Landmark Theatres {{acquired}} <b>the</b> <b>Ritz</b> Theatre Group in Philadelphia {{which consisted}} of <b>the</b> <b>Ritz</b> East, <b>Ritz</b> <b>at</b> <b>the</b> Bourse and <b>Ritz</b> V. Landmark opened their flagship theater in Los Angeles, The Landmark. Later that year, Landmark also opened Harbor East in Baltimore and The Landmark Theatre, Greenwood Village in Denver.|$|R
