50|$|Butt-Numb-A-Thon is held {{annually}} in Austin, Texas, {{for the first}} eight years <b>at</b> <b>the</b> Alamo Drafthouse's (now closed) original downtown location at 409 Colorado St. In 2007, BNAT 9 was held <b>at</b> <b>the</b> Alamo Drafthouse <b>Ritz</b> location at 310 E. Sixth Street. Since 2008, the festival has been held <b>at</b> <b>the</b> Alamo Drafthouse South Lamar at 1120 South Lamar Boulevard. BNAT 15 in 2013 was held <b>at</b> <b>the</b> Alamo Drafthouse <b>Ritz</b> location while <b>the</b> Alamo Drafthouse Lamar underwent renovation.|$|R
